---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="labs — luqmaan.dev"
  description="Agents Assemble: Hulm Club Tech Guild workshop labs. Connect an agent to the real world, write skills, and build your own workflows."
>
  <main class="page">
    <header class="site-header">
      <a href="/" class="site-logo">luqmaan.dev</a>
      <a href="/connect" class="nav-link">connect →</a>
    </header>

    <h1 class="labs-title">Agents Assemble</h1>
    <p class="labs-event">Hulm Club Tech Guild — 1 April 2026</p>

    <p class="labs-intro">
      Tonight you'll go from assistant to agent. Your agent will walk you through three labs — you just need to get it set up and hand it the skill file. It'll take it from there.
    </p>

    <section class="labs-setup">
      <h2 class="labs-heading">Get Set Up</h2>

      <p class="labs-text">Pick your tool, then run the install command below to give your agent the workshop skill.</p>

      <div class="setup-path">
        <h3 class="setup-name">Claude Code</h3>
        <p class="setup-desc">For Anthropic Max / Pro subscribers.</p>
        <div class="setup-warning">
          <strong>Privacy:</strong> Claude Code may use your conversations to improve Claude by default.
          To turn this off: open Claude Code → type <code>/config</code> → go to <strong>Privacy</strong> → disable <strong>"Improve Claude"</strong>.
        </div>
        <div class="setup-install">
          <p class="setup-label">Install the workshop skill:</p>
          <pre><code>curl -sL https://luqmaan.dev/skills/agents-assemble.md \
  -o ~/.claude/commands/agents-assemble.md</code></pre>
          <p class="setup-label">Then in Claude Code, type:</p>
          <pre><code>/agents-assemble</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="setup-path">
        <h3 class="setup-name">OpenCode</h3>
        <p class="setup-desc">Free and open-source. Works with free models via OpenRouter.</p>
        <div class="setup-warning warning-caution">
          <strong>Data warning:</strong> If you're using free models through OpenRouter, your prompts are sent to third-party model providers. <strong>Do not enter sensitive personal data, passwords, or private information.</strong> Your data may be used for training by the model provider.
        </div>
        <div class="setup-install">
          <p class="setup-label">Install the workshop skill:</p>
          <pre><code>curl -sL https://luqmaan.dev/skills/agents-assemble.md \
  -o ~/.opencode/skills/agents-assemble.md</code></pre>
          <p class="setup-label">Then start OpenCode and ask it to:</p>
          <pre><code>Run the agents-assemble skill</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="labs-overview">
      <h2 class="labs-heading">The Labs</h2>
      <p class="labs-text">Your agent will guide you through each of these. The detail is in the skill file — here's the overview.</p>

      <div class="lab-card">
        <span class="lab-number">01</span>
        <h3 class="lab-name">Connect to Something Real</h3>
        <p class="lab-desc">
          Give your agent a browser. It'll open a real webpage, navigate it, read the content, and do something useful with what it finds. You'll see it happen live.
        </p>
        <p class="lab-time">~25 min</p>
      </div>

      <div class="lab-card">
        <span class="lab-number">02</span>
        <h3 class="lab-name">Make It Repeatable</h3>
        <p class="lab-desc">
          Take what you just did and write it as a skill — a plain-English recipe your agent can follow on command. No code. Just instructions.
        </p>
        <p class="lab-time">~25 min</p>
      </div>

      <div class="lab-card">
        <span class="lab-number">03</span>
        <h3 class="lab-name">Define Your Own</h3>
        <p class="lab-desc">
          Think about a real workflow from your life or work. Build a skill for it. This one's yours.
        </p>
        <p class="lab-time">~15 min</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="labs-wifi">
      <h2 class="labs-heading">WiFi</h2>
      <p class="labs-text">
        <strong>SSID:</strong> HulmClubMembers<br/>
        <strong>Password:</strong> 123salam
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>

<style>
  .labs-title {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .labs-event {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #777777;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .labs-intro {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #000000;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .labs-heading {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .labs-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #777777;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .labs-setup {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .setup-path {
    border: 1px solid #E4E4E4;
    padding: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .setup-name {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .setup-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #777777;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .setup-warning {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #000000;
    background: #f5f5f5;
    padding: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .setup-warning code {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    background: #E4E4E4;
    padding: 1px 4px;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .warning-caution {
    background: #fff8e1;
  }

  .setup-install {
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .setup-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #777777;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .setup-install pre {
    background: #1a1a1a;
    color: #e0e0e0;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .setup-install pre code {
    background: none;
    padding: 0;
    color: inherit;
    font-size: inherit;
  }

  .labs-overview {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .lab-card {
    padding: 20px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #E4E4E4;
  }

  .lab-card:first-of-type {
    border-top: 1px solid #E4E4E4;
  }

  .lab-number {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #E53935;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .lab-name {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #000000;
    margin: 4px 0 8px;
  }

  .lab-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #777777;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .lab-time {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #777777;
  }

  .labs-wifi {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .labs-wifi .labs-text strong {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
  }
</style>
